  "strategy": [
    "Alternate between short forward moves and committed scans/rotations to maximize marker detection.",
    "After each forward commit, enforce a scan to avoid missing the marker.",
    "On obstacle detection, recover with backward or rotation, then scan before resuming forward.",
    "Use commit states for all rotations and forward moves to avoid oscillations and ensure action completion.",
    "Prioritize marker pursuit: when marker_seen, switch to marker_pursuit and move directly toward the marker.",
    "When marker_close, stop to safely complete the task.",
